data.description: This property features a huge backyard paradise with no Back Neighbors! Brand New ROOF!!!  3367 Sq Ft Home is one of the largest in the neighborhood with 5 bedrooms and 3 1/2 bathrooms. Zone X flood zone and home has never flooded.  Big 500+sq ft swimming pool with slide and firepits. Sizeable storage building included. Covered patio and mature palm trees add to the beautifully landscaped backyard.  Enjoy Gorgeous sunsets in the evenings under the stars of your own private oasis. Inside you'll find an huge living room, wired for home theater next to a cozy fireplace and large tile floors ready for your oversized furniture. Upstairs has brand new carpet. Need a game room, lots of bedrooms, big kitchen, formal dining plus an office?  This home has it all! Fridge with double ice-maker included. Lot is over 14,400 sq ft!  Double-oven and built-in microwave makes cooking a joy.  The chef of the home will also like the large center island. How about an HOA only $150 a year! Low tax rate too!
